Downgrade from 3.5.5 to 3.1.0
Bad things will happen if you skip step 3 and perform step 6 immediately. 
1) Download 3.1.1 Intermittent Version and 3.1.0 Stable Version and copy them onto  
the phone
2) Boot into recovery
3) Flash OnePlus2Oxygen14OTA021all1610121102wipe9505656273ba4203.zip 
4) Reboot into ROM
5) Boot into Recovery
6) Flash OnePlus2Oxygen14OTA020all1608262242_44a55e674a2b4bf6.zip
7) Reboot
You should now have successfully downgraded to OOS 3.1.0
